    • getActivity

      public String getActivity()
      Return activity of this license.

      Sodir description:
      Name of the licensing activity the production licence was awarded in.

      varchar(40), corresponds to Sodir property prlLicensingActivityName.

      Returns:
      Activity of this license. Null if N/A or unknown.

    • getMainArea

      public String getMainArea()
      Return main area of this license.

      Sodir description:
      Name of the area on the Norwegian Continental Shelf where the wellbore is located. Example of legal values:

      • Barents Sea
      • Norwegian Sea
      • North Sea

      varchar(40), corresponds to Sodir property prlMainArea.

      Returns:
      Activity of this license. Null if N/A or unknown.

      Return status of this license.

      • INACTIVE

      varchar(40), corresponds to Sodir property prlStatus.

      Returns:
      Status of this license. Null if N/A or unknown.

    • getStratigraphical

      public String getStratigraphical()
      Return the stratigraphical state of this license.

      Sodir description:
      Indicates if the license has vertical limitations based on stratigraphy. 'NO' means no such limitations, 'YES OR PARTLY' means that either whole or parts of the license has such limitations.

      varchar(40), corresponds to Sodir property prlStratigraphical.

      Returns:
      Stratigraphical state of this license. Null if N/A or unknown.
